QuestData.Title: Other Interests
QuestData.Description:
Madam Goya is interested in many unusual items other than just rare metals.
Keep your eyes out for these particular items during your travels in Nazjatar.
Deliver them to me and Madam Goya will consider you for special access.
QuestData.LogDescription: Deliver $1oa Disintegrating Sand Sculpture to Steelsage Gao.
